metadata.name: Don't be shy.
metadata.description:
【Theme of this piece】
The cuteness that lurks within the coolness.
I thought that a direct cute expression is not the only way to express "cute," so I used a combination of colors, gestures, and facial expressions.

【About my work...】
I make my works with the aim of being "cute" anyway. I express various gestures, facial expressions, clothes, backgrounds, etc., to create the "cute" that I want.
If you are looking for the same "cuteness" as me, please take a look at my works. You will love it.
